{"tid":2292250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我代連登仝人，以表最高嘅尊榮，願榮光稱歸中大","createTime":"2020-11-19T10:51:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T11:09:50.000Z","uid":56984,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"85fef1911eea4658da62accc8457e08c4cdcd46d","tid":2292250,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:51:26.000Z","msg":"今日暴大畢業典禮，<br />\n令我諗返曾經青春嘅日子<br />\n當聽到願榮光<br />\n當聽到光復香港<br />\n當大家都仲未放棄<br />\n我諗返一年前嘅我哋係幾咁青春熱血<br />\n佢地付出咗日後會比人拉嘅勇氣<br />\n去繼續呢一個一世人得一次嘅畢業典禮<br />\n<br />\n我哋前路仲係未明朗<br />\n或者有生之年都未必見到光復之日<br />\n但今日中大手足話我地聽<br />\n<br />\n這一場革命<br />\n最終無人取勝<br />\n但請你，請你，留低一起作見證。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">光復香港 ! 願榮光歸香港! </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"35324a15f1e050285b60ea2e9dee3a9dae82b017","tid":2292250,"uid":356238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:52:06.000Z","msg":"又係我，我係未來人，100%侵將會贏，侵輸咗，我會派10000比留名者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2270510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2270510</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n還錢未啊，屌你老母未來人"},{"pid":"a6dfa21d8da5291ca7a117c2c74b41a3f017f4b1","tid":2292250,"uid":56984,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:52:13.000Z","msg":"有感而發，因為見到中大手足，我不禁流下眼淚"},{"pid":"2657ca1b2b99f6630205ae82cec98542c70ccee0","tid":2292250,"uid":56984,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"35324a15f1e050285b60ea2e9dee3a9dae82b017","tid":2292250,"uid":356238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:52:06.000Z","msg":"又係我，我係未來人，100%侵將會贏，侵輸咗，我會派10000比留名者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2270510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2270510</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n還錢未啊，屌你老母未來人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:52:35.000Z","msg":"今日放埋一邊先"},{"pid":"d27527ce300d3f4f9fd0d5c02578dd389bf3076a","tid":2292250,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:52:55.000Z","m